{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":4000,"text":"What's in the box?"},{"time":7000,"text":"Whatever it is must be pretty important,"},{"time":9000,"text":"because I've traveled with it, moved it,"},{"time":12000,"text":"from apartment to apartment to apartment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":15000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":17000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20000,"text":"Sound familiar?"},{"time":23000,"text":"Did you know that we Americans"},{"time":25000,"text":"have about three times the amount of space"},{"time":27000,"text":"we did 50 years ago?"},{"time":29000,"text":"Three times."},{"time":32000,"text":"So you'd think, with all this extra space,"},{"time":35000,"text":"we'd have plenty of room for all our stuff."},{"time":38000,"text":"Nope."},{"time":40000,"text":"There's a new industry in town,"},{"time":42000,"text":"a 22 billion-dollar, 2.2 billion sq. ft. industry:"},{"time":45000,"text":"that of personal storage."},{"time":47000,"text":"So we've got triple the space,"},{"time":49000,"text":"but we've become such good shoppers"},{"time":52000,"text":"that we need even more space."},{"time":55000,"text":"So where does this lead?"},{"time":57000,"text":"Lots of credit card debt,"},{"time":59000,"text":"huge environmental footprints,"},{"time":62000,"text":"and perhaps not coincidentally,"},{"time":64000,"text":"our happiness levels flat-lined over the same 50 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67000,"text":"Well I'm here to suggest there's a better way,"},{"time":70000,"text":"that less might actually equal more."},{"time":73000,"text":"I bet most of us have experienced at some point"},{"time":75000,"text":"the joys of less:"},{"time":78000,"text":"college -- in your dorm,"},{"time":81000,"text":"traveling -- in a hotel room,"},{"time":84000,"text":"camping -- rig up basically nothing,"},{"time":86000,"text":"maybe a boat."},{"time":88000,"text":"Whatever it was for you, I bet that, among other things,"},{"time":91000,"text":"this gave you a little more freedom,"},{"time":93000,"text":"a little more time."},{"time":96000,"text":"So I'm going to suggest"},{"time":98000,"text":"that less stuff and less space"},{"time":100000,"text":"are going to equal a smaller footprint."},{"time":102000,"text":"It's actually a great way to save you some money."},{"time":104000,"text":"And it's going to give you a little more ease in your life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107000,"text":"So I started a project called Life Edited at lifeedited.org"},{"time":110000,"text":"to further this conversation"},{"time":112000,"text":"and to find some great solutions in this area."},{"time":115000,"text":"First up: crowd-sourcing my 420 sq. ft. apartment in Manhattan"},{"time":119000,"text":"with partners Mutopo and Jovoto.com."},{"time":122000,"text":"I wanted it all --"},{"time":124000,"text":"home office, sit down dinner for 10,"},{"time":127000,"text":"room for guests,"},{"time":129000,"text":"and all my kite surfing gear."},{"time":131000,"text":"With over 300 entries from around the world,"},{"time":134000,"text":"I got it, my own little jewel box."},{"time":137000,"text":"By buying a space that was 420 sq. ft."},{"time":139000,"text":"instead of 600,"},{"time":142000,"text":"immediately I'm saving 200 grand."},{"time":145000,"text":"Smaller space is going to make for smaller utilities --"},{"time":148000,"text":"save some more money there,"},{"time":151000,"text":"but also a smaller footprint."},{"time":153000,"text":"And because it's really designed"},{"time":155000,"text":"around an edited set of possessions -- my favorite stuff --"},{"time":157000,"text":"and really designed for me,"},{"time":159000,"text":"I'm really excited to be there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"So how can you live little?"},{"time":163000,"text":"Three main approaches."},{"time":165000,"text":"First of all, you have to edit ruthlessly."},{"time":168000,"text":"We've got to clear the arteries of our lives."},{"time":171000,"text":"And that shirt that I hadn't worn in years?"},{"time":174000,"text":"It's time for me to let it go."},{"time":176000,"text":"We've got to cut the extraneous out of our lives,"},{"time":179000,"text":"and we've got to learn to stem the inflow."},{"time":182000,"text":"We need to think before we buy."},{"time":184000,"text":"Ask ourselves,"},{"time":186000,"text":"\"Is that really going to make me happier? Truly?\""},{"time":189000,"text":"By all means,"},{"time":191000,"text":"we should buy and own some great stuff."},{"time":193000,"text":"But we want stuff that we're going to love for years,"},{"time":196000,"text":"not just stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"Secondly, our new mantra:"},{"time":200000,"text":"small is sexy."},{"time":202000,"text":"We want space efficiency."},{"time":204000,"text":"We want things that are designed"},{"time":206000,"text":"for how they're used the vast majority of the time,"},{"time":208000,"text":"not that rare event."},{"time":210000,"text":"Why have a six burner stove"},{"time":212000,"text":"when you rarely use three?"},{"time":214000,"text":"So we want things that nest,"},{"time":216000,"text":"we want things that stack, and we want it digitized."},{"time":219000,"text":"You can take paperwork,"},{"time":221000,"text":"books, movies,"},{"time":223000,"text":"and you can make it disappear -- it's magic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":226000,"text":"Finally, we want multifunctional spaces and housewares --"},{"time":230000,"text":"a sink combined with a toilet,"},{"time":232000,"text":"a dining table becomes a bed --"},{"time":234000,"text":"same space,"},{"time":236000,"text":"a little side table"},{"time":238000,"text":"stretches out to seat 10."},{"time":240000,"text":"In the winning Life Edited scheme in a render here,"},{"time":243000,"text":"we combine a moving wall with transformer furniture"},{"time":245000,"text":"to get a lot out of the space."},{"time":247000,"text":"Look at the coffee table --"},{"time":249000,"text":"it grows in height and width"},{"time":251000,"text":"to seat 10."},{"time":253000,"text":"My office folds away,"},{"time":255000,"text":"easily hidden."},{"time":257000,"text":"My bed just pops out of the wall with two fingers."},{"time":260000,"text":"Guests? Move the moving wall,"},{"time":263000,"text":"have some fold-down guest beds."},{"time":265000,"text":"And of course, my own movie theater."}]},{"cues":[{"time":268000,"text":"So I'm not saying that we all need to live"},{"time":270000,"text":"in 420 sq. ft."},{"time":272000,"text":"But consider the benefits of an edited life."},{"time":275000,"text":"Go from 3,000 to 2,000,"},{"time":277000,"text":"from 1,500 to 1,000."},{"time":280000,"text":"Most of us, maybe all of us,"},{"time":282000,"text":"are here pretty happily for a bunch of days"},{"time":284000,"text":"with a couple of bags,"},{"time":286000,"text":"maybe a small space, a hotel room."},{"time":288000,"text":"So when you go home and you walk through your front door,"},{"time":291000,"text":"take a second and ask yourselves,"},{"time":293000,"text":"\"Could I do with a little life editing?"},{"time":295000,"text":"Would that give me a little more freedom?"},{"time":297000,"text":"Maybe a little more time?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":301000,"text":"What's in the box?"},{"time":304000,"text":"It doesn't really matter."},{"time":307000,"text":"I know I don't need it."},{"time":310000,"text":"What's in yours?"},{"time":312000,"text":"Maybe, just maybe,"},{"time":314000,"text":"less might equal more."},{"time":316000,"text":"So let's make room"},{"time":318000,"text":"for the good stuff."}]},{"cues":[{"time":320000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":322000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}